name: Brenda Stephen
description: I am simple, easy going, confident and caring. I can also say i am kind, charming, honest, polite, promising and truthful. I love making those around me happy. I like having fun with friends and also I love meeting new people. I do not descriminate and I give equal respect to everyone and anyone. I dislike cheating, jealousy, lies and most of all pessimism. I am very easy to get along with and I am a kindhearted person. I have said enough for now, the rest will be know later personally.
